@cindex In the money curses
@cindex At the money curses
@cindex Time bleeding curses
The option model will begin pricing. The updating pricing changes are the result of time bleeding between the current time and the expiration times. Inputs can be adjusted while the model is pricing. Try typing: @kbd{S, s, X, x, R, r, V, v} or the arrow keys.
